## Day 6: Learning useEffect + Life lesson (BIG WIN)

## useEffect in React
useEffect is like onload effect in javascript, it is a React Hook that let a component react to changes or perform side effects.
it's also a way to run code automatically when something happens in my component.

## How to use it
useEffect(() => {
  // code to run will be written here.
});

